                                    "text": "There are many types of descriptors, each focused on trying to characterize or summarize some meaningful aspect of sound. Some of these may be perceptually relevant and some may be more computationally relevant, but each has its strengths and weaknesses. Here are some of the descriptor types in Data Knot."
