                                    },
                                    "text": "Descriptors can be computed on a single onset or in a continuous manner, depending on what you want to achieve. When extracting descriptors from singular events or doing corpus-based matching, onset-based descriptor anlaysis is what you want. When using descriptors to map ongoing descriptor analysis to other parameters like in regression or direct mapping, realtime descriptor analysis is what you want."
